pos_mean_info_list.mean: 失望的，沮丧的；受挫折的
令人失望的；令人扫兴的
令人失望（disappoint的ing形式）；辜负…的期望

bilingual.target: 这次旅行并没有使失望。

bilingual.source: I don't want to disappoint my parents.
bilingual.target: 我不想使失望我的父母。

bilingual.source: His behavior will surely disappoint his friends.
bilingual.target: 他的行为肯定会使失望他的朋友们。

bilingual.source: I don't want to disappoint my parents with my grades.
bilingual.target: 我不想用我的成绩使失望我的父母。

bilingual.source: The weather forecast might disappoint those planning a picnic.
bilingual.target: 天气预报可能会使失望那些计划野餐的人。

bilingual.source: She promised not to disappoint her team in the final match.
bilingual.target: 她承诺在决赛中不会使失望她的队伍。

bilingual.source: The movie didn't disappoint; it was as good as everyone said.
bilingual.target: 这部电影没有使失望；它和大家说的一样好。

bilingual.source: Movies also disappoint us when things don't look the way we imagined them in the books.
bilingual.target: 当电影中的事物与我们在书中想象的不一样时，电影也会让我们失望。

bilingual.source: She tends to crucify her friends when they disappoint her.
bilingual.target: 当朋友让她失望时，她倾向于严厉批评他们。

bilingual.source: The much-anticipated sequel did not disappoint the audience.
bilingual.target: 这部备受期待的续集没有让观众失望。

list.abstract: Disappoint（英 [ˌdɪsəˈpɔɪnt]，美 [ˌdɪsəˈpɔɪnt]），英语单词。作动词为使…失望；使（希望；期望）破灭。例句：In order not to disappoint her, Huang thought of the idea of a mobile classroom（为了不让她失望，黄想到了移动教室的想法）。 近义词有fail，let down。

yingyinNormal.en: Do not think for one moment that you'll disappoint me. I will love you, no matter what.
yingyinNormal.zh: 任何时刻都别认为你会让我失望。我将爱你，无论怎样。

yingyinNormal.en: I'll say this for you, Katniss. You don't disappoint. Well, Plutarch gave me a letter for you. I don't want it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我必须得说，凯特尼斯，你从不让人失望，普鲁塔什让我给你带了封信。我不想看。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm sorry to disappoint you, but this isn't love. All Mr. Wise wants from me is to make him a legionnaire again.
yingyinNormal.zh: 很抱歉让你失望了，因为这不是爱情。怀斯先生只是想利用我回到军队而已。

yingyinNormal.en: It's been pretty well talked up, so my expectations were mighty high. But still, it, did not disappoint. Not a bit.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那儿的景色被人津津乐道，所以我的期待非常高。不过那里还是没让我失望。一点也不。

yingyinNormal.en: I've told you, Bernard. Never place your trust in us. We're only human. Inevitably, we will disappoint you. Good-bye, my friend.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我跟你说过了，伯纳德，永远不要相信我们，我们只是人类，我们不可避免地会让你失望，再见，我的朋友。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay look, do you have anything Christmassy? I promised my son, and I really don't want to disappoint him, come on, you gotta have something.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，有没有什么比较算是圣诞节的？我答应了我儿子，不想让他失望，你们一定有的。

yingyinNormal.en: I don't like food. I love it. If I don't love it, I don't swallow. I will return tomorrow night with high expectations. Pray you don't disappoint me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不只爱好美食，我热爱美食，如果我不热爱，就根本吞不下肚。明晚我会满怀期待回到这里。向天祈祷吧! 你最好别让我失望。

yingyinNormal.en: Actually, I do. My mother is pushing for my brother, Georgie, to be my best man, and I hate to disappoint her again. I already rejected her savior and her LinkedIn invitation.
yingyinNormal.zh: 其实我还真了解。我妈妈想要我让我哥，小乔治来当我的伴郎，我不愿意但也不想再拒绝她。我已经拒绝了她的救主以及领英网邀请了。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: The "threatened" tag <highlight>disappointed</highlight> some environmentalists in that it went against conservation policies.
examination_example.sentence_trans: “受到威胁”的标签让一些环保主义者失望，因为它违背了保护政策。
